s/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt">CD Projekt</a>使用人工智能重新创建了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cyberpunk-2077"><em>《赛博朋克 2077》</em></a>推出后去世的演员的声音，以便开发者可以在游戏最近发布的扩展包中重复使用他的角色。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/phantom-liberty-is-a-stunning-swan-song-for-cyberpunk-2077-3500337">《幻影自由》是《赛博朋克 2077》的绝妙绝唱</a></strong></li></ul><p>Miłogost Reczek 在游戏的波兰本地化版本中为开膛手 Viktor Vektor 配音。他还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-witche"><em>《巫师》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-witcher-3"><em>《巫师 3：狂猎》</em></a>中饰演维塞米尔和泰勒，在<em>《巫师 2：国王刺客》</em>中饰演巴兰·拉瓦宁·金博尔特和泰勒的间谍，在<em>《巫师 3：狂猎</em>》的资料片《<em>石之心》</em>中饰演凯斯塔提斯冯·埃弗雷克.</p><p> Reczek 于 2021 年去世，之后<em>《赛博朋克 2077</em> 》的资料片<a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-launch-timezone-console-pc-3499805"><em>《幻影自由》</em></a>于 2022 年底揭晓<em>。《幻影自由》</em>允许玩家为自己的角色添加更多网络软件，如果超出限制，他们会收到来自 Vektor 的电话来纠正他们的错误。条件并重置他们的增强。 </p><figure id="attachment_3514685" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514685" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514685" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514685" class="wp-caption-text"> 《赛博朋克 2077》扩展包《幻影自由》图片来源：CD Projekt</figcaption></figure><p> CD Projekt 在接受<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-12/video-game-cyberpunk-2077-uses-ai-to-replace-deceased-voice-actor?leadSource=uverify%20wall"><em>彭博社</em></a>采访时表示，“这样做已经得到了 Reczek 家人的许可”，并且团队在改变路线之前“考虑在资料片中替换他，并在原版游戏中重新录制他的台词”，这样他们就不会重铸Vektor。</p><p> “我们不喜欢这种做法，”CD Projekt 的本地化总监 Mikołaj Szwed 在谈到用其他演员取代 Reczek 时说道。</p><p> Szwed 表示 Reczek 是“波兰最好的配音人才之一”，他在<em>《赛博朋克 2077》中的表现“非常出色”。</em></p><p>他还补充说，演员的儿子们“非常支持”重现已故父亲的声音并再次在故事中出演的计划。 </p><figure id="attachment_3514686" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514686" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514686" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cyberpunk-2077-dev-used-AI-to-recreate-actors-voice-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514686" class="wp-caption-text"> 《赛博朋克 2077》扩展包《幻影自由》图片来源：CD Projekt</figcaption></figure><p>该团队通过使用名为 Respeecher 的语音克隆软件实现了这一目标。另一位演员在<em>《Phantom Liberty》</em>中录制了 Vektor 的台词，然后将 Reczek 的“语音样本池”输入到 Respeecher，让人工智能能够创建算法。</p><p>该算法将录音中另一位演员的声音更改为雷切克的声音。</p><p>本地化项目经理 Marta Cannilla 上个月表示，<a href="https://youtu.be/96BwQ7rHS_A?t=1066" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这是开发商“向他致敬”以及他的贡献的方式，</a>以确保他仍然是游戏未来的一部分。</p><p>其他游戏新闻方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>收购<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">动视暴雪</a>的交易已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsofts-acquisition-of-activision-blizzard-has-been-approved-by-all-regulators-3514539">获得竞争与市场管理局的批准</a>，这意味着该交易不再存在任何障碍。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-used-ai-to-recreate-a-late-actors-voice-for-phantom-liberty-3514657">《赛博朋克 2077》使用人工智能为《幻影自由》重现已故演员的声音，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
