 Easy Life 在英国最终演出之前以当前名称分享“信任练习” https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-share-trust-exercises-ahead-of-final-uk-shows-under-current-name-3514656?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=easy-英国决赛前的生活共享信任练习以当前名称显示Liberty DunworthFri, 13 Oct 2023 10:12:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3514656 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="轻松生活，2023 年。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此前，乐队因其名字而面临 EasyJet 的法律诉讼</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-share-trust-exercises-ahead-of-final-uk-shows-under-current-name-3514656">Easy Life 在英国决赛之前分享的“信任练习”帖子以当前名称</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="轻松生活，2023 年。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Easy-Life-Press-Shot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/easy-life">Easy Life</a>分享了一首名为“Trust Practices”的新单曲，这是他们以当前乐队名称发行的最后一张专辑。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/murray-matravers-on-easy-lifes-rise-if-youre-enjoying-and-healthy-in-your-mind-that-for-me-is-succes-3489941">默里·马特拉弗斯 (Murray Matravers) 谈 Easy Life 的崛起：“如果你享受它并且头脑健康，对我来说这就是成功”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该曲目于今天早上（10 月 13 日）分享，现已通过 Island Records 发售，标志着莱斯特五人组将以 Easy Life 名义发行的新音乐的最后一部分。</p><p>继昨晚（10 月 12 日）在家乡莱斯特的 O2 学院举行告别演出后，今晚晚些时候他们将在伦敦 Koko 场地举行告别演出，门票已全部售完。这两场演出都是针对最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-say-theyre-being-sued-by-easyjet-over-their-name-3507949">成员因乐队名称而面临 EasyJet 授权公司 EasyGroup 的法律诉讼</a>。</p><p>与 Finneas 一起制作的《Trust Practices》是一首被乐队视为一个完整循环的时刻，也是他们最古老、最珍贵的歌曲之一，其灵感来自于与好人在一起并尊重他人。</p><p> “《Trust Practices》的发行时间紧迫，但音乐性永恒，为莱斯特乐队结束了一个篇章，同时巩固了其作为这一代最重要（且不可阻挡）英国乐队之一的声誉，”一份新闻稿中写道。看看下面的曲目。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：信任练习" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3NEPYiw4V5tmQLguweXgPP?si=7b276f15bc9249bc&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>这支由 Murray Matravers、Oliver Cassidy、Sam Hewitt、Lewis Berry 和 Jordan Birtles 组成的乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-to-release-final-single-trust-exercises-under-band-name-after-losing-easygroup-battle-3513244">于本周早些时候首次预告了最后一首歌曲</a>，当时他们在 Instagram 官方页面上分享了这首歌的片段。</p><p> “这首歌是我六年多前写的。从那时起，我进行了无数的更改/编辑/调整，”阅读标题。 “我们一直在等待合适的时机放弃这首歌，但感觉从来都不是合适的，新材料总是优先考虑的。</p><p> ​​“我们终于把我们的东西整合在一起，我们计划在一月份发行它，但是，我们只有到周五才能以 Easy Life 的形式发布任何音乐，”它补充道。 “我们已经制作了黑胶唱片和周边商品，上面印满了 Easy Life，所以现在就实现，机不可失。”</p><p>这场骚乱首先出现在本月初，当时成员们透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-say-theyre-being-sued-by-easyjet-over-their-name-3507949">他们被该集团起诉，</a>并声称该公司“强迫”他们更改名字，否则将面临代价高昂的法律诉讼。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CyQv655MS9P/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.